1. *Pa* dođi večeras u klub (So, come to the club tonight).
2. On je *pa* odlučio da se vrati kući (So, he decided to go home).
3. *Pa*, nisam ni znao da je to uradio (Well, I didn't even know he did that).
4. *Pa*, možemo da pričamo o tome sutra (Well, we can talk about it tomorrow).
5. *Pa* hajde da probamo nešto novo (Well, let's try something new).